{"data":[{"date":"16:19 28/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng n\u1eef C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhung-nu-cdv-bong-da-quyen-ru-nhat-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3872","checkdouble":"189852"},{"date":"16:46 28/06","title":"Sao H\u00e0n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f3 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/28/sao-han-tung-bung-mung-chien-thang-kho-tin-truoc-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Park Shin Hye, Hwang Seung Eun v\u1ee1 \u00f2a khi tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eafng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014. </h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Hinh-anh-sao-Han-mung-chien-thang-Han-Quoc-2-0-Duc-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ca s\u0129 Bae Ki Sung v\u00e0 b\u00e0 x\u00e3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat h\u1ed3i h\u1ed9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh tivi khi theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i 27/6. Tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, anh vi\u1ebft \"Win\" \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Hwang-Seung-Eun-7841-1530156279.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Hwang Seung Eun tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \"c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0110\u1ee9c\". Hwang Seung Eun cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f4 v\u1ee1 \u00f2a c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \"h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o, bi\u1ebft \u01a1n\" c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/haha-9199-1530156279.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <p class=\"Image\">Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean, ca s\u0129 Haha chia s\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 k\u00e8m bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng  \"b\u1eafn tim\" \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 sung s\u01b0\u1edbng\u00a0khi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. </p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/yoona-4258-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <p class=\"Image\">Yoona \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh to\u00e0n  \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.\u00a0C\u00f4 vi\u1ebft: \"C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n\u00a0th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3  l\u00e0m h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh\". </p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Untitled-5-9634-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ji Sook \u0111\u0103ng \u1ea3nh chung cu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, k\u00e8m theo chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i \u0111ang kh\u00f3c\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/lee-su-bin-6850-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Lee Su Bin vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Instagram: \"G\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00e1c anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c anh l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/park-shin-hye-5037-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p Park Shin Hye vi\u1ebft: \"N\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u01a1i. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/jung-hae-in-2554-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0\"Trai \u0111\u1eb9p\" Jung Hae In: \"T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng. C\u00e1c anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u00e1c anh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/sao-1-4115-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ca s\u0129 Jo Kwon: \"C\u00e1c anh \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 r\u1ed3i. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/yoon-3791-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Yoon Kyun Sang: \"\"N\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 tu\u00f4n r\u01a1i. D\u00f9 cho c\u00e1c anh kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c - m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi - th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00fang ta chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. T\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta. G\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 - c\u00e1c anh s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u1edbn m\u1ea1nh n\u1eefa. K\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u, quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Rain-7255-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ca s\u0129, di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Rain, \u00f4ng x\u00e3 c\u1ee7a Kim Tae Hee: \"Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1ea5y Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. R\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/phan-ung-trai-chieu-cua-cdv-duc-vs-han-quoc-sau-tran-cau-lich-su-461-189855.html\">Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuoi-dau-ruot-voi-hang-loat-anh-che-ve-that-bai-cua-dt-duc-421-189850.html\">C\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-dt-duc-dong-goi-hanh-ly-len-duong-ve-nuoc-421-189848.html\">Video: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i h\u00e0nh l\u00fd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-dan-anh-ha-he-sau-that-bai-e-che-cua-tuyen-duc-421-189839.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Anh h\u1ea3 h\u00ea sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u00ea ch\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-nhuc-nha-roi-world-cup-ca-the-gioi-noi-gi-421-189837.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c cay \u0111\u1eafng r\u1eddi World Cup, c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-duc-bi-che-nhao-ra-sao-sau-khi-som-thanh-cuu-vuong-world-cup-421-189834.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o ra sao sau khi s\u1edbm th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3871","checkdouble":"189857"},{"date":"16:08 28/06","title":"Martial, Morata v\u00e0 Icardi s\u1eafp s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/28/martial-morata-va-icardi-sap-sat-canh-ben-canh-nhau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, Alvaro Morata, v\u00e0 Mauro Icardi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Tuttosport \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 mua 3 sao kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 mua 3 sao kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/Chuyen-nhuong-Juventus-2018-mua-3-sao-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGonzalo Higuain l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Chelsea, HLV Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp thay th\u1ebf Conte mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. PSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 nh\u1eafm Higuain thay Cavani.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaulo Dybala c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Real v\u00e0 Liverpool l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca th\u00ec quan t\u00e2m Miralem Pjanic, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean ra \u0111i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1ebd b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus nh\u1eafm 3 sao l\u1edbn thay th\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Tuttosport, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, Alvaro Morata, v\u00e0 Mauro Icardi \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 ba Higuain, Dybala v\u00e0 Pjanic.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/martial-morata-va-icardi-sap-sat-canh-ben-canh-nhau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus nh\u1eafm Morata v\u00e0 Martial n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Anthony Martial v\u00e0 Alvaro Morata l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Martial \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U th\u00ec Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Morata \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRi\u00eang tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Mauro Icardi th\u00ec kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n b\u1edfi Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan kh\u00f4ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong c\u00f9ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Emre Can theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3870","checkdouble":"189847"},{"date":"14:25 28/06","title":"HAGL m\u1ea5t C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League v\u00ec \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/27/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a V-League sau khi \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong HAGL vs Than Quang Ninh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Ng\u1ecdc Ch\u00e2u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a HAGL do \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. \u00c1n ph\u1ea1t n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Qu\u1ea3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc song h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Tam K\u1ef3. T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 3 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 4.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3 l\u1ea1i mang t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p cho HAGL, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m 3-2 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018. Khi \u1ea5y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap k\u00e8m th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, khi m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c trong nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3869","checkdouble":"189842"},{"date":"15:14 28/06","title":"Atletico Madrid b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n \"h\u00fat m\u00e1u\" Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/atletico-madrid-bat-ngo-muon-hut-mau-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Cesar Azpilicueta c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd quan t\u00e2m Cesar Azpilicueta\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAtletico Madrid \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, sau khi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Thomas Lemar c\u1ee7a Monaco, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Cesar Azpilicueta  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Cesar Azpilicueta  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/atletico-madrid-bat-ngo-muon-hut-mau-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Atletico h\u1ecfi mua Azpilicueta\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/dai-gia-la-liga-chinh-thuc-so-huu-thomas-lemar-voi-gia-khung-180-188349.html\" target=\"_blank\">Atletico mua Lemar th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span>, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. El Gol Digital \u0111\u01b0a tin, Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Cesar Azpilicueta c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 20 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1nh v\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Atletico s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Cesar Azpilicueta</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Atletico mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Cesar Azpilicueta l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. El Gol Digital kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y kinh ph\u00ed chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Joao Miranda t\u1eeb Inter Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ESPN chi ra rang chi con Azpilicueta muon chien dau cho Antonio Conte.\" title=\"ESPN ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n Azpilicueta mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho Antonio Conte.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/Antonio-Conte-va-cuoc-chuyen-giao-chang-em-dep-tai-Etihad-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Azpilicueta \u0111\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu trung v\u1ec7, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y Azpilicueta \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Azpilicueta c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea t\u1eeb Marseille v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford anh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3868","checkdouble":"189844"},{"date":"15:49 28/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! 2 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Mourinho mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/20/day-2-vi-tri-ma-mourinho-muon-bo-sung-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Mourinho mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ed Woodward \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, MU \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i mua s\u1eafm t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mua trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mua trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-2018-mua-trung-ve-va-cau-thu-chay-canh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Fred v\u00e0 Dalot</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-mu-cong-bo-tan-binh-fred-172-189182.html\" target=\"_blank\"> MU mua Fred</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Traford. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecf ra 19 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dalot t\u1eeb Porto.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Young v\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo t\u1edd The Times \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c t\u00e2n binh Dalot c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1nh khi\u1ebfn Mourinho t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n 2 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Mourinho mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Mourinho mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ed Woodward \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mua trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 mua trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/day-2-vi-tri-ma-mourinho-muon-bo-sung-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Eric Bailly. Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, ngo\u00e0i ra c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Bonucci c\u1ee7a AC Milan hay Clement Lenglet c\u1ee7a Sevilla.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean M.U s\u1ebd chi kho\u1ea3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Anthony Martial mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Mourinho mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, hi\u1ec7n \u00f4ng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea ho\u1eb7c Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 60 tri\u1ec7u euro, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 M.U d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9ng 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua Gareth Bale. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3867","checkdouble":"189846"},{"date":"11:34 28/06","title":"Tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o ra sao sau khi s\u1edbm th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng World Cup","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/28/tuyen-duc-bi-che-nhao-ra-sao-sau-khi-som-thanh-cuu-vuong-world-cup.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u0110V t\u1eeb Brazil, Anh hay Mexico \