h\u1ecd th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/c4-1530135095_680x0.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u00e1 c\u1edd H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa l\u00e1 c\u1edd Mexico, nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Trung M\u1ef9. Nh\u1edd chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Son Hyun-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Mexico may m\u1eafn l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 d\u00f9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd h\u1ecd th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"- Ngay 27/6/2010, Frank Lampard bi tu choi ban thang vao luoi tuyen Duc tai vong 1/8 World Cup. Tuyen Anh that bai 1-4. - Ngay 27/6/2018, Duc bi Han Quoc loai khoi vong bang World Cup. Nguoi Anh ha he.\" title=\"- Ng\u00e0y 27/6/2010, Frank Lampard b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup. Tuy\u1ec3n Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-4. - Ng\u00e0y 27/6/2018, \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh h\u1ea3 h\u00ea.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/c3-1530135301_680x0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">- Ng\u00e0y 27/6/2010, Frank Lampard b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup. Tuy\u1ec3n Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-4. - Ng\u00e0y 27/6/2018, \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh h\u1ea3 h\u00ea.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"To Fox Sports phien ban Brazil cuoi ha he khi chung kien Duc xep cuoi bang F World Cup 2018. Nguoi Brazil van chua nguoi noi dau that bai 1-7 truoc Duc o ban ket World Cup 2014.\" title=\"T\u1edd Fox Sports phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Brazil c\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ea3 h\u00ea khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngu\u00f4i n\u1ed7i \u0111au th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2014.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/c2-1530135165_680x0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u1edd Fox Sports phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Brazil c\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ea3 h\u00ea khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngu\u00f4i n\u1ed7i \u0111au th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2014.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3866","checkdouble":"189834"},{"date":"09:50 28/06","title":"Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a SLNA</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/7_zing.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap SLNA h\u1ea1 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ch\u1ec9 trong 10 ph\u00fat, t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 56 \u0111\u1ebfn 66, </span>tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap SLNA ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2 chung cu\u1ed9c.</span> \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i t\u1eeb ph\u00eda HLV \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV T\u00e0i Em ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201cT\u00f4i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, n\u00ean d\u1eb7n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c k\u1ef9 c\u1eadu ta. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ebfc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 hay v\u00e0 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. C\u1eadu ta thu\u1ed9c d\u1ea1ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn gi\u1eef phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i h\u1ed3i x\u01b0a\u2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 6 n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t may anh \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng SLNA v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, SLNA l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi b\u1ecf xa nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf v\u1edbi 20 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y, c\u1eeda tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/27/SLNA-3-2-Sai-Gon.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189729.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189729.html\">SLNA 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (KT): Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, CLB x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 H\u1ed3 Ph\u00fac T\u1ecbnh trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn SLNA c\u00f3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Qua \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3865","checkdouble":"189826"},{"date":"10:13 28/06","title":"\u0110\u00e1 k\u00e9m, ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u1ee7a HAGL s\u1edbm b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/da-kem-ngoai-binh-cua-hagl-som-bi-thanh-ly.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario Gordon \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i chia tay CLB HAGL \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>CLB HAGL ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Rimario Gordon l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB HAGL s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 sung s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 c\u1ee7a HAGL. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ban \u0111\u1ea7u, ngo\u1ea1i binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e1 k\u00e9m, ngo\u1ea1i binh Rimario s\u1edbm b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e1 k\u00e9m, ngo\u1ea1i binh Rimario s\u1edbm b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/thi-dau-kem-hieu-qua-ngoai-binh-cua-hagl-sap-bi-thanh-ly.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ngo\u1ea1i binh Rimario b\u1ecb HAGL ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Kh\u00f4ng ghi n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u1ea1i V-League, Rinario c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 n\u00f3ng t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn HAGL quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thanh l\u00fd anh trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sau v\u00f2ng 16 V-League, BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Rimario. V\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00f4ng qua trang facebook c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. 6 th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao. D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i chia tay nhau nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i\", Rimario vi\u1ebft. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i Rimario, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Osmar Francisco. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Brazil t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d nh\u01b0ng qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i do Osmar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c 'li h\u00f4n' Rimario th\u00ec CLB HAGL c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Kim Jin-seo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\">HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3864","checkdouble":"189830"},{"date":"11:32 28/06","title":"Sau v\u00f2ng 16 V-League: HAGL g\u1ecdi, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/27/sau-vong-16-vleague-hagl-goi-ha-noi-tra-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 HAGL v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>\u2018G\u1ed7\u2019 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, HAGL ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 CLB c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean BXH. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o n\u1ed9i binh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai s\u1edbm c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau pha b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 16 V-League HAGL g\u1ecdi, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 16 V-League HAGL g\u1ecdi, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau khi D\u01b0\u01a1ng Thanh H\u00e0o nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf sau pha truy c\u1ea3n V\u0103n To\u00e0n ghi b\u00e0n, HAGL ghi th\u00eam 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-0 chung cu\u1ed9c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HAGL \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c tinh th\u1ea7n to l\u1edbn gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/26/HAGL-4-0-Quang-Ninh.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, ph\u00e1o \u0111\u00e0i b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 x\u00e2m ph\u1ea1m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. G\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111ang sa s\u00fat, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Samson m\u1edbi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 13 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gia t\u0103ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng. Sau v\u00f2ng 16, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp sau t\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y d\u00f9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 10 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi vs Quang Nam\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/ha-noi-vs-quang-nam-vong-16-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i to\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Thanh H\u00f3a th\u0103ng hoa<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn thua H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 0-2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 12 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 lo l\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady n\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u 13 sau khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111\u00e3 \u2018h\u1ed3i sinh\u2019 v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, r\u1ed3i XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0 Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ghi 7 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n, v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean BXH, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i v\u1edbi FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u tho\u00e1t b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Thanh H\u00f3a hay SLNA, CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. L\u00fac n\u00e0y Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111ang c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t cao, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB TP.HCM \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 15. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t hi v\u1ecdng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0103n S\u1ef9 s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o h\u01a1n khi ghi t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong chu\u1ed7i 4 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong \u0111\u00f3 3 tr\u1eadn gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i, CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 12, t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 v\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 TP.HCM v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam d\u00f9 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng 16, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111ang x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 12/14 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i. \u1ede v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u2018chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c\u2019 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau vong 16\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 16\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Untitled.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 16</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\">HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3863","checkdouble":"189833"},{"date":"11:18 28/06","title":"Trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2016/7/20/hlv-conte-khang-dinh-ngung-theo-duoi-koulibaly.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kalidou Koulibaly c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y trung v\u1ec7 Kalidou Koulibaly \u0111\u00e3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Napoli, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 hay nh\u1ea5t Serie A \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Koulibaly\" title=\"hau ve Koulibaly\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/6/chu-tich-napoli-tiet-lo-gia-khung-chelsea-moi-chao-de-co-koulibaly.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Koulibaly \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 gi\u00fap anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Napoli nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba chia tay Napoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n The Blues chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/trung-ve-nay-khien-chelsea-phai-chi-65-trieu-bang-o-he-2018-172-184925.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Koulibaly</span>, song ph\u00eda Napoli v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu t\u00f4i c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro th\u00ec b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Napoli v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f2n chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai do ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i lo li\u1ec7u. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft k\u1ef9 h\u01a1n h\u00e3y h\u1ecfi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kalidou Koulibaly tin Senegal s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Senegal \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Colombia. Kalidou Koulibaly tin Senegal s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Kalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Kalidou-Koulibaly-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Koulibaly tin Senegal s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Senegal \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 tu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng sau Senegal, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3862","checkdouble":"189829"},{"date":"18:14 27/06","title":"Sao Barca tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/27/rafinha-muon-roi-barca-cang-som-cang-tot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Inter Milan d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t Rafinha sau 1 n\u0103m m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Barcelona. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Rafinha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t Rafinha</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Inter Milan quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u01b0\u1ee3n Rafinha v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Barcelona k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 38 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea1i CLB m\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb HLV Luciano Spalletti. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n17 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i Serie A, Rafinha ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ed9ng 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Radja Nainggolan t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Giuseppe Meazza c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho c\u1eeda \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rafinha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rafinha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/rafinha-muon-roi-barca-cang-som-cang-tot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rafinha kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i Inter</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 cha ki\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Rafinha, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Mazinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng Inter kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t anh. \u201c<em>Th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 5 th\u00e1ng 6 v\u1eeba qua</em>\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Gazzetta dello Sport. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>B\u00e2y gi\u1edd con trai t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Inter mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef n\u00f3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh tay h\u01a1n</em>.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca th\u1eadt s\u1edbm</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRafinha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Barcelona. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 48 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i La Liga cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m 2017, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Rafinha \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Rafinha\" title=\"tien ve Rafinha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/9/Inter-Milan-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tien-ve-Rafinha-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rafinha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMazinho kh\u00f4ng tin con trai m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Rafinha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. \u201c<em>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i ch\u1edd Inter. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t</em>.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>La Liga, Premier League, Ligue 1 v\u00e0 Bundesliga \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Serie A. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rafinha v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi trong m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1edbi. M\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Barcelona</em>.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-va-real-muon-mua-thiago-alcantara-180-189489.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca vs Real v\u00ec sao tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea-172-189414.html\">Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sao-man-city-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-barca-180-189345.html\">Sao Man City c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-barca-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189276.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-mua-sao-mu-sau-su-ra-di-cua-iniesta-180-189268.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua sao M.U sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3861","checkdouble":"189772"},{"date":"16:17 27/06","title":"Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n h\u1ed9p \u0111\u00eam tho\u00e1t y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/tuyen-anh-o-khach-san-gan-hop-dem-thoat-y-chuan-bi-cho-tran-gap-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u0110V x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 lo l\u1eafng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 con c\u01b0ng kh\u00f3 ng\u1ee7 b\u1edfi ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Kaliningrad.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 4 sao ForestMix Club \u1edf ng\u00f4i l\u00e0ng nh\u1ecf Repino, thu\u1ed9c St Petersburg l\u00e0m n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n. Sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Southgate ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0103n ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 28/6 t\u1edbi.<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n h\u1ed9p \u0111\u00eam tho\u00e1t y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n h\u1ed9p \u0111\u00eam tho\u00e1t y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/anh1-4970-1530082802.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tuy\u1ec3n Anh ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n 1.000km \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9. \u1ea2nh: Mirror.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Kaliningrad, n\u01a1i di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00e1ch b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf Repino t\u1edbi 1.000km. Trong th\u1eddi gian l\u01b0u tr\u00fa t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Radisson - n\u1eb1m ngay g\u1ea7n qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n l\u00e0 h\u1ed9p \u0111\u00eam tho\u00e1t y mang t\u00ean Maxim.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 lo ng\u1ea1i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Southgate s\u1ebd b\u1ecb l\u00e0m phi\u1ec1n b\u1edfi ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n. \"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ecdn n\u01a1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0m ch\u1ed1n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fac v\u00e0 \u1ed3n \u00e0o t\u1edbi sau n\u1eeda \u0111\u00eam. Qu\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng Pobedy ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u01a1i c\u00e1c fan t\u1ee5 t\u1eadp v\u00e0 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 xem c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ed9p \u0111\u00eam tho\u00e1t y b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u1edbi m\u1edf g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f4ng kh\u00e1ch. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00ecn t\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3\", Ivan Torbinski - m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u00e2n trong v\u00f9ng - chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi t\u1edd Mirror.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nD\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 5.000 C\u0110V Anh t\u1edbi Kaliningrad \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9. Do hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t, nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hop dem thoat y Maxim doi dien khach san noi tuyen Anh thue. Anh: Mirror.\" title=\"H\u1ed9p \u0111\u00eam tho\u00e1t y Maxim \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n n\u01a1i tuy\u1ec3n Anh thu\u00ea. \u1ea2nh: Mirror.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/thoat2-5940-1530082802.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u1ed9p \u0111\u00eam tho\u00e1t y Maxim \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n n\u01a1i tuy\u1ec3n Anh thu\u00ea. \u1ea2nh: Mirror.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3860","checkdouble":"189747"}]}